items.badge_description: Thanks for staying at home, and checking in with Untappd! It allows us to stay connected to a community of beer lovers, just like you, even if we can't be in the same physical location. From our home to yours, cheers and stay safe!

While spontaneity can be fun, sometimes you want to make sure your adventure will rock. Checkout the menu at an Untappd Verified Venue before visiting and know exactly what’s on tap! That's 385 check-ins at venue that is verified.  Try 5 more for Level 78!
99 bottles of beer on the wall, 99 bottles of beer. Take one down, pass it around.... That's 290 checkins with the serving style of Bottle. Try 5 more for Level 59!
Happy Untappd anniversary to you! Thanks for sticking around and drinking socially with us. Cheers! That's 8 years on Untappd!
After a long day, what better way to kick back than with a crisp and refreshing lager? You're already feeling more relaxed, aren’t you?. That’s 375 different Lagers! Try 5 more for Level 76!

items.checkin_comment: Вот вроде ничего особенного совершенно, а вроде и нормально. Как будто бы дортмунд лагер по вкусу привычен как наше местное пиво. Солодово, слегка травянисто, немного криспи. Стоит отметить, оно было на исходе своих дней.

We love lagers! Crisp, clean, cold fermenting, these beers are a labor of love. Whether a dark Dunkel, a malty amber, or a light helles, lagers never fail us. So on Lager Day, join us in a toast to the humble lager.
